text: Hla Myint () may also refer to: * Hla Myint (1920–2017), Burmese economist * Hla Myint (brigadier general) (born c. 1948), former mayor of Yangon (2011–2016), former brigadier-general in Myanmar Army * Hla Myint Swe (minister), former Minister of Transport, Myanmar * Hla Myint Swe (artist) (born 1948), Burmese artist
title: Hla Myint (disambiguation)
